## 4. Cache Poisoning / Unkeyed Headers (Param Miner territory)

Yeh headers server response ko affect karte hain but cache key mein include nahi hote.

- `X-Forwarded-Host` тАФ Reflected in links тЖТ cache poisoning risk
- `X-Forwarded-Scheme` тАФ Protocol confusion
- `X-Original-URL` тАФ Routing bypass
- `X-Rewrite-URL` тАФ Routing bypass
- `X-HTTP-Method-Override` тАФ Method confusion
- `X-Forwarded-Server` тАФ Backend info leak
- `Accept-Charset` тАФ Sometimes unkeyed, response variation
- `X-Wap-Profile` тАФ Legacy, sometimes unkeyed

> Note: Param Miner scan platacard.mx pe 6 unkeyed headers discover kar chuka hai тАФ un findings ko yahan ki list ke against verify karo (reflected XSS via header ya cache poisoning chain ban sakta hai).

