## 5. WAF Bypass Headers (Cloudflare-specific)

- **X-Forwarded-For with malicious payload**
  WAF sirf body/URL check karta hai, header nahi тАФ kabhi bypass milta hai

- **Case randomization**
  `sELEct` instead of `SELECT` in header values

- **Content-Type confusion**
  `application/json` тЖТ `text/plain;application/json`

- **Chunked transfer encoding**
  Request smuggling attempts via `Transfer-Encoding: chunked`

- **Header order randomization**
  Kuch WAFs specific header order expect karte hain

- **Null byte injection**
  `%00` in header values

- **Unicode normalization**
  Full-width characters se filter bypass

> Reminder: Cloudflare aggressively configured hai platacard.mx pe тАФ X-Original-URL aur X-Forwarded-Host already blocked test kiye ja chuke hain.

