## 7. CORS Misconfiguration Testing

**Test 1 тАФ Null origin**
Send: `Origin: null`
Secure response should NOT reflect `Access-Control-Allow-Origin: null`

**Test 2 тАФ Arbitrary origin**
Send: `Origin: https://evil.com`
Secure response should NOT reflect this back

**Test 3 тАФ Subdomain trust abuse**
Send: `Origin: https://evil.target.com`
Secure server should NOT blindly trust wildcard subdomains

**Test 4 тАФ Credentials check**
Check if `Access-Control-Allow-Credentials: true` AND reflected origin dono present hain тАФ is combo se critical vuln milta hai

