## 8. Rate Limiting Bypass

- **IP rotation via header** тАФ `X-Forwarded-For: <random_ip>` per request
- **Alternate IP headers** тАФ Rotate between `X-Real-IP`, `X-Client-IP`, `True-Client-IP`
- **User-Agent rotation** тАФ `User-Agent: <random>`
- **Session/Cookie removal** тАФ Agar rate-limit session-based hai (IP-based nahi) to cookie remove karke reset try karo

