## 9. Burp Suite Workflow

1. **Intercept** request in Proxy тЖТ send to **Repeater** (`Ctrl+R`)
2. Repeater mein header add/modify karo manually, ek-ek karke test karo
3. **Param Miner** extension тЖТ right-click тЖТ "Guess headers" for automated unkeyed header discovery (UAT scope only automated ke liye)
4. **Intruder** тЖТ Sniper attack type тЖТ header value ki jagah payload position set karo тЖТ wordlist load karo
5. Response diff check karo тАФ status code, response length, reflected content sab compare karo

